         </listRelation>
         <div type="edition">
           <note>
             This division into textparts and incipits follow <ref type="mss" corresp="BLorient757"></ref>
           </note>
           <div type="textpart" xml:id="IsaiahOfScete">
             <label>Extract from Isaiah of Scete</label>
             <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
               <ab>
                 ጥንተ፡ ቃል፡ እምነገረ፡ ጻድቅ፡ ኢሳይያስ፡ ወእንዘ፡ ሀሎኩ፡ አነ፡ በ፩ጊዜ፡ እምጊዜያት፡ ንቡረ፡ በጥቃ፡ ገቦሁ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ መቃርዮስ፡
                 መጽኡ፡ ጉባዔ፡ አኃው፡ እምሀገረ፡ እስክንድርያ። ከመ፡ ይስአልዎ፡ ሎቱ፡ እንዘ፡ ይብሉ፡ ንግረነ፡ ኦአቡነ፡ ዘከመ፡ እፎ፡ ንድኅን።
               </ab>
             </div>
           </div>
           <div type="textpart" xml:id="JohnClimacus">
             <label>Extract from John Climacus of Mount Sinai</label>
             <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
               <ab>
                 ነገረ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ገባሬ፡ መንክራት፡ ዘደብረ፡ ሲና፡ እንዘ፡ ይብል፡ ወበ፩ እምጊዜያት፡ እንተ፡ ሀሎኩ፡ ንቡረ፡ ውስተ፡ ገዳም፡
                 ውሣጣዊት፡ ወመጽአ፡ ኀቤየ፡ ፩ እምአኃው፡ ለሕዋፄ፡ እምነ፡ ደብር፡ ወተስእልክዎ፡ ዘከመ፡ እፎ፡ ሀለዉ፡ በደህና፡ በጸሎትክሙ፡
                 ወፈድፋደሰ፡ ተስእልክዎ፡ በእንተ፡ እኅው፡ ዘሰማዕኩ፡ ሕሠመ፡ ምግባሩ፤ ወይቤለነ፡
               </ab>
             </div>
           </div>
           <div type="textpart" xml:id="Sayings1">
             <label>Sayings of Isaiah, ʾAbbā Bamnu (Poemen?), and Theodore</label>
           </div>
           <div type="textpart" xml:id="Albatariqun1">
             <label>Extract <foreign xml:lang="gez">እምነ፡ እልበታሪቁን፡</foreign></label>
           </div>
           <div type="textpart" xml:id="Sayings2">
             <label>Sayings of Poemen <foreign xml:lang="gez">አብ፡ ባውሚን፡</foreign>, Pachomius
           <foreign xml:lang="gez">አቡነ፡ ጳኩሚስ፡</foreign>, and other Egyptian Fathers.
              </label>
           </div>
           <div type="textpart" xml:id="Albatariqun2">
             <label>Extract <foreign xml:lang="gez">እምነ፡ እልበታሪቁን፡</foreign>
           </label>
           </div>
           <div type="textpart" xml:id="JohnCrysostom">
             <label>Extract from John Chrysostom on the Gospel of St John</label>
           </div>
           <div type="textpart" xml:id="Theodosius">
             <label>Extract from Theodosius</label>
             <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
               <ab>
                 ቴዎዶስዮስ፡ ዘየአቢ፡ ዘአስቈባኒ፡ ሶበ፡ ሐለየ፡ በሕሊናሁ፡ ቃለ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ዘይብል፡ እስመ፡ ውእቱ፡ ኮነ፡ ይትጌበር፡ መዓልተ፡
                 ወሌሊተ፡ ከመ፡ ኢይኩን፡ ክበደ፡ ለመኑሂ፡ ወኮነት፡ ተግባረ፡ እዴሁ፡ ተአክሎ፡ ሎቱ።
               </ab>
             </div>
           </div>
           <div type="textpart" xml:id="Gannata">
             <label>Extract from <foreign xml:lang="gez">እምገነተ፡ አበው፡</foreign>
           </label>
           </div>
           <div type="textpart" xml:id="Zena">
             <label>Extract from <foreign xml:lang="gez">እምዜና፡ አብ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዮሐንስ፡</foreign></label>
           </div>
           <div type="textpart" xml:id="Evagrius1" corresp="LIT2121OntheE">
             <label>Evagrius on the eight evil passions</label>
           </div>
           <div type="textpart" xml:id="Evagrius2" corresp="LIT2121OntheE">
             <label>Extract from Evagrius</label>
           </div>
         </div>
